---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service — SiteGenius"
  description="SiteGenius terms of service. The terms and conditions that govern our web design services."
>
  <article class="pt-32 pb-24">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-black mb-4">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-muted-300 text-sm mb-12">Last updated: April 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none space-y-10">

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-muted-100 mb-4">1. Agreement to Terms</h2>
          <p class="text-muted-200 leading-relaxed">By using any service provided by SiteGenius ("we", "us", "our"), including our website at sitegenius.co.nz, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree, please do not use our services.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-muted-100 mb-4">2. Services</h2>
          <p class="text-muted-200 leading-relaxed mb-4">SiteGenius provides web design, web development, website hosting, and related digital services. Specific deliverables, timelines, and pricing are agreed upon in writing (via email or quote) before work commences.</p>
          <p class="text-muted-200 leading-relaxed">We reserve the right to decline any project at our discretion.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-muted-100 mb-4">3. Hosting &amp; Ongoing Services</h2>
          <p class="text-muted-200 leading-relaxed mb-4">Where ongoing services (hosting, care plans, email) are arranged separately, the following terms apply:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-muted-200">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-neon-cyan mt-1">→</span><span>Ongoing services are billed monthly in advance</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-neon-cyan mt-1">→</span><span>Services may be cancelled with 30 days written notice</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-neon-cyan mt-1">→</span><span>No refunds are issued for partial months</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-neon-cyan mt-1">→</span><span>We reserve the right to suspend hosting for accounts overdue by more than 14 days</span></li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-muted-100 mb-4">4. One-Time Projects</h2>
          <p class="text-muted-200 leading-relaxed mb-4">For fixed-price project builds:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-muted-200">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-neon-cyan mt-1">→</span><span>A deposit (typically 50%) is required before work begins</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-neon-cyan mt-1">→</span><span>The remaining balance is due before the website goes live</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-neon-cyan mt-1">→</span><span>Deposits are non-refundable once work has commenced</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-neon-cyan mt-1">→</span><span>Scope changes may incur additional charges</span></li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-muted-100 mb-4">5. Client Responsibilities</h2>
          <p class="text-muted-200 leading-relaxed mb-4">To deliver your project on time, you agree to:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-muted-200">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-neon-cyan mt-1">→</span><span>Provide required content, images, and information in a timely manner</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-neon-cyan mt-1">→</span><span>Respond to review requests within a reasonable timeframe</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-neon-cyan mt-1">→</span><span>Ensure all content provided is legally owned or licensed by you</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-neon-cyan mt-1">→</span><span>Not use our services for any unlawful or harmful purpose</span></li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-muted-100 mb-4">6. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p class="text-muted-200 leading-relaxed">Upon full payment, you own the website content and design created specifically for you. SiteGenius retains the right to display completed work in our portfolio. We retain ownership of any proprietary tools, code libraries, or frameworks used in development.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-muted-100 mb-4">7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p class="text-muted-200 leading-relaxed">To the maximum extent permitted by New Zealand law, SiteGenius shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from the use of our services. Our total liability shall not exceed the amount paid by you in the 3 months preceding the claim.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-muted-100 mb-4">8. Uptime and Hosting</h2>
          <p class="text-muted-200 leading-relaxed">We aim for 99.9% uptime on all hosted websites but do not guarantee uninterrupted service. Scheduled maintenance will be communicated in advance where possible. We are not liable for downtime caused by third-party infrastructure providers.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-muted-100 mb-4">9. Governing Law</h2>
          <p class="text-muted-200 leading-relaxed">These terms are governed by the laws of New Zealand. Any disputes will be resolved under the jurisdiction of New Zealand courts.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-muted-100 mb-4">10. Contact</h2>
          <p class="text-muted-200 leading-relaxed">For any questions about these terms, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@sitegenius.co.nz" class="text-neon-cyan hover:underline">hello@sitegenius.co.nz</a>.</p>
        </section>

      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
